channel.title: Help needed really much!@!@
channel.description:
Dear people,
Can someone help me? I have a server and i can play it on my client, the problem is, my friends cant play it. Not on mopar,silabsoft or just the client itself..
Please help! :eek:

item.title: Help needed really much!@!@
item.dc:creator: @Mr_Bobby Mr. Bobby
item.description:
@Mr_Bobby wrote:

chances are its not assigned to your ip, look for either “127.0.0.1” “0.0.0.0” “localhost” without the quotes in either your client.java,gui.java(if you have it) or egui.java(if you have it).

All of this is client side
